   Colorado Works Program
     * Temporary Cash Assistance to qualifying families
     * Employment Assistance

   Food Stamps
     * Supplemental Food Assistance
     * Employment First Program

   Low Income Childcare Assistance
     * Subsidized Childcare assistance
     * Contracted Providers

   Low Income Energy Assistance Program (LEAP)
     * Pays winter home heating costs
     * Weatherization assistance

   Family & Children's Medicaid
     * Healthcare Coverage
     * Physicians Services
     * Family Planning

   Fraud & Recovery Program
     * Investigates & Prosecutes Welfare Fraud
     * Determines & Collects overpayment amounts
